# Commands Used in the Project

## 1. Navigate to Prometheus Directory

```bash
cd prometheus-3.12.0.darwin-arm64
```

## 2. Check Prometheus Configuration

```bash
./promtool check config prometheus.yml
```

## 3. Start Prometheus

```bash
./prometheus --config.file=prometheus.yml
```

## 4. Verify Prometheus Process

```bash
ps -ef | grep prometheus
```

## 5. Open Prometheus UI

```text
http://localhost:9090
```

## 6. Check Prometheus Targets

```text
http://localhost:9090/targets
```

## 7. Navigate to Node Exporter Directory

```bash
cd node_exporter-1.11.1.darwin-arm64
```

## 8. Start Node Exporter

```bash
./node_exporter
```

## 9. Verify Node Exporter Process

```bash
ps -ef | grep node_exporter
```

## 10. Verify Metrics Endpoint

```bash
curl http://localhost:9100/metrics | head
```

## 11. Verify Prometheus Target Status

```bash
curl http://localhost:9090/api/v1/targets
```

## 12. View Prometheus Configuration

```bash
cat prometheus.yml
```

## 13. Edit Prometheus Configuration

```bash
nano prometheus.yml
```

## 14. Stop Prometheus

```bash
Ctrl + C
```

## 15. Stop Node Exporter

```bash
Ctrl + C
```

