# PromQL Queries Used

## Check Target Health

```promql
up
```

## CPU Metrics

```promql
node_cpu_seconds_total
```

## Memory Available

```promql
node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes
```

## Memory Usage

```promql
node_memory_MemTotal_bytes - node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes
```

## Filesystem Metrics

```promql
node_filesystem_size_bytes
```

## Network Metrics

```promql
node_network_receive_bytes_total
```

## Process Metrics

```promql
process_resident_memory_bytes
```

